### Removing special character
def removing_special_character(t):
    y = []
    for i in t:
        if i.isalnum():
            y.append(i)
    return y
In [38]:
df['Transform text'] = df['Transform text'].apply(removing_special_character)

### Removing stop words 
def Removing_stop_words(t):
    y = []
    for i in t:
        if i not in stopwords.words('english'):
            y.append(i)
    return y
In [43]:
df['Transform text']=df['Transform text'].apply(Removing_stop_words)

In [45]:
### Removing Punctuations
def Remove_punctuations(t):
    y = []
    for i in t:
        if i not in string.punctuation:
            y.append(i)
    return y
In [46]:
df['Transform text']=df['Transform text'].apply(Remove_punctuations)
In [47]:
### Stemming
from nltk.stem.porter import PorterStemmer
ps = PorterStemmer()
def stemming_of_text(t):
    y = []
    for i in t:
        y.append(ps.stem(i))
    return " ".join(y)
In [48]:
df['Transform text'] = df['Transform text'].apply(stemming_of_text)
